illed%20the%20gap.%20From%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20through%20August%2C%20tech%20exports%20to%20the%20US%20from%20countries%20like%20South%20Korea%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20and%20India%20jumped%2080%25%2C%20according%20to%20Goldman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20US%2C%20Chinese%20tech%20exports%20didn't%20suffer%20the%20same%20fate.%20Demand%20in%20Europe%2C%20Asia%2C%20and%20emerging%20markets%20kept%20growing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTech%20exports%20to%20non-US%20destinations%20showed%20little%20difference%20between%20China%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20Asia%2C%20with%20tech%20exports%20from%20both%20performing%20similarly%20well%20compared%20to%20other%20sectors%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Goldman's%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20China%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20Asia's%20tech%20exports%20to%20non-US%20markets%20rose%20about%2020%25%20relative%20to%20the%20fourth%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20%26quot%3Breflecting%20strength%20in%20global%20tech%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman's%20analysts%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tariffs%20underscore%20how%20Washington's%20trade%20war%20is%20reshaping%20supply%20chains%20and%20driving%20high-tech%20decoupling%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20divergence%20also%20reflects%20a%20bigger%20trend%3A%20a%20steady%20reordering%20of%20tech%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-trade-war-covid-companies-moving-supply-chains-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esupply%20chains%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20accelerated%20during%20the%20pandemic%20and%20has%20been%20reinforced%20by%20Washington's%20trade%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20nearly%20half%20of%20the%20US's%20critical%20tech%20imports%20came%20directly%20from%20China.%20By%202025%2C%20that%20figure%20has%20fallen%20below%2020%25%2C%20Goldman%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaiwan%2C%20Mexico%2C%20Japan%2C%20India%2C%20and%20Vietnam%20have%20gained%20market%20share%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2284b666d4-dcb2-4c22