E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMiraculously%2C%20it%20all%20worked%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20first%20term%2C%20Trump%20criticized%20the%20H-1B%20program%20and%20signed%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-executive-orders-memorandum-proclamations-presidential-action-guide-2017-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202017%20that%20ordered%20federal%20agencies%20to%20review%20and%20propose%20changes.%20That%20year%2C%20Nadella%20called%20reviewing%20the%20program%20a%20%26quot%3Bgood%20idea%26quot%3B%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20Marketplace's%20%26quot%3BMake%20Me%20Smart%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20country%20should%20look%20at%20their%20immigration%20policy%20and%2C%20especially%20in%20this%20case%2C%20it's%20about%20American%20competitiveness%2C%26quot%3B%20Nadella%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BAt%20least%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20when%20we%20think%20about%20H-1B%2C%20it's%20mostly%20about%20high-skilled%20labor%20that%20allows%20us%2C%20an%20American%20company%2C%20to%20be%20globally%20competitive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EElon%20Musk%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Elon%20Musk%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20of%20the%20White%20House%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20on%20May%2030%2C%202025%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68b6f614194a2d49b8af8c7f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222813%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EElon%20Musk%20has%20long%20argued%20that%20falling%20birth%20rates%20are%20the%20greatest%20threat%20to%20civilization.%3Cp%3EALLISON%20ROBBERT%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20a%20strong%20advocate%20for%20the%20H-1B%20visa%2C%20said%20that%20he%20once%20held%20the%20visa%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20was%20born%20in%20South%20Africa%20and%20came%20to%20the%20US%20to%20study%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%20in%201992.%20He%20became%20a%20US%20citizen%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20according%20to%20biographies%20of%20the%20billionaire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20October%20X%20post%2C%20Musk%20said%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bon%20a%20J-1%20visa%20that%20transitioned%20to%20an%20H1-B.%26quot%3B%20The%20J-1%20visa%20is%20for%20research%20scholars%2C%20professors%2C%20and%20students%20participating%20in%20programs%20that%20promote%20cultural%20exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20set%20of%20posts%20on%20X%20in%20December%2C%20Musk%20defended%20the%20H-1B%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20reason%20I'm%20in%20America%20along%20with%20so%20many%20critical%20people%20who%20built%20SpaceX%2C%20Tesla%20and%20hundreds%20of%20other%20companies%20that%20made%20America%20strong%20is%20because%20of%20H1B%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20go%20to%20war%20on%20this%20issue%20the%20likes%20of%20which%20you%20cannot%20possibly%20comprehend%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJayshree%20Ullal%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jayshree%20Ullal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d06c8ff9db348adc0be455%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3E%3A%20Scott%20Mlyn%2FCNBC%2FNBCU%20Photo%20Bank%2FNBCUniversal%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJayshree%20Ullal%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20Arista%20Networks%2C%20a%20cloud%20networking%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20London%20and%20raised%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Ullal%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20to%20study%20engineering%20at%20San%20Francisco%20State%20University%20and%20Santa%20Clara%20University.%20She%20worked%20at%20Fairchild%20Semiconductor%2C%20Advanced%20Micro%20Devices%2C%20and%20Cisco%20before%20her%20role%20at%20Arista%20Networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%20pegged%20her%20net%20worth%20at%20%246.4%20billi