0new%20cargo%20plane%20as%20an%20airlift%20option%20for%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Windrunner%20is%20supposed%20to%20easily%20carry%20four%20modern%20fighter%20jets%20or%20six%20Chinooks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20it's%20only%20released%20renderings%2C%20Radia%20previously%20announced%20an%20R%26amp%3BD%20partnership%20with%20the%20Pentagon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20late-stage%20startup%20building%20the%20world's%20largest%20plane%20%E2%80%94%20originally%20for%20moving%20giant%20wind%20turbine%20blades%20%E2%80%94%20now%20wants%20its%20aircraft%20to%20ferry%20Chinooks%20and%20fighter%20jets%20for%20the%20US%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Windrunner%20is%20meant%20to%20offer%2012%20times%20the%20cargo%20space%20of%20Boeing's%20C-17%20Globemaster%20III%2C%20the%20Pentagon's%20primary%20heavy-lift%20carrier%2C%20according%20to%20Radia%2C%20its%20maker%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fradia-worlds-largest-cargo-plane-wind-turbine-blades-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebased%20in%20Boulder%2C%20Colorado%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release%20on%20Friday%20that%20it%20was%20proposing%20its%20product%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bultra-large%20air%20cargo%20aircraft%26quot%3B%20for%20moving%20weapons%20platforms%20and%20transports.%20It%20originally%20built%20the%20Windrunner%20to%20airlift%20wind%20turbine%20fan%20blades%20as%20long%20as%20330%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20wingspan%20of%20261%20feet%20and%20a%20length%20of%20356%20feet%2C%20the%20Windrunner%20is%20supposed%20to%20carry%20payloads%20as%20long%20as%20344%20feet%2C%20as%20wide%20as%2033%20feet%2C%20and%20as%20tall%20as%20nearly%2030%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222799%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Radia%20WindRunner%20in%20a%20field%20surrounded%20by%20wind%20turbines.%20It%20is%20unloading%20a%20giant%20turbine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6605c24a3f923f7dab0255e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERadia%20wants%20to%20ship%20giant%20turbines%20around%20the%20world%20via%20a%20behemoth%20cargo%20plane%20called%20WindRunner.%3Cp%3ERadia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20would%20make%20Radia's%20plane%20larger%20than%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fantonov-an-225-mriya-worlds-largest-cargo-plane-history-details-2020-4%23it-is-not-clear-why-the-one-of-a-kind-plane-was-destroyed-whether-it-was-a-deliberate-attack-or-collateral-damage-of-the-russian-invasion-but-kuleba-says-its-destruction-will-not-ruin-ukraines-dream-of-freedom-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAntonov%20An-225%20Mriya%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Soviet%20Union's%20sole%20gargantuan%20cargo%20plane%20with%20six%20engines.%20The%20An-22%20held%20the%20record%20as%20the%20world's%20biggest%20aircraft%2C%20but%20was%20destroyed%20during%20a%20battle%20in%20Ukraine%20in%20April%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERadia%20lists%20the%20Windrunner's%20payload%20weight%20as%20roughly%20160%2C000%20pounds%2C%20which%20is%20less%20than%20the%20smaller%20C-17's%20170%2C900%20pounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20firm%20wrote%20in%20its%20press%20release%20that%20it's%20trying%20to%20solve%20the%20problem%20of%20cargo%20volume%20for%20the%20military.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModern%20joint%20capabilities%20frequently%20run%20out%20of%20space%20before%20they%20run%20out%20of%20lift%2C%26quot%3B%20Radia%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20the%20Windrunner's%20size%20would%20allow%20it%20to%20carry%20up%20to%20four%20fighter%20jets%2C%20such%20as%20the%20F-16%20Fighting%20Falcon%20or%20the%20F-35C%20Lightning%20II%20Joint%20Strike%20Fighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlternatively%2C%20the%20Windrunner%20is%20supposed%20to%20carry%20six%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fch-47-chinook-helicopter-army-photos-tour-2018-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECH-47%20Chinooks%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20disassembling%20any%20of%20the%2098-foot-long%20transports.%20Currently%2C%20these%2018-foot-tall%20helicopters%20need%20to%20have%20their%20rotors%20removed%20to%20be%20transported%20by%20air%2C%20or%20they%20would%20be%20too%20tall%20to%20fit%20in%20the%20US%20military's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-air-force-plans-to-keep-c5-cargo-planes-flying-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EC-5%20Super%20Galaxy%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20C-17.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20its%20maximum%20payload%2C%20the%20Windrunner%20is%20meant%20to%20fly%20at%20a%20range%20of%201%2C200%20miles%2C%20which%20is%20just%20under%20the%20F-35C's%201%2C350%20miles.%20The%20C-17%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20has%20a%20full%20payload%20range%20of%20about%202%2C760%20miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERadia%20also%20wants%20the%20Windrunner%20to%20take%20off%20and%20land%20on%20unpaved%20runways%20as%20short%20as%206%2C000%20feet.%20Today's%20larger%20military%20cargo%20planes%20typically%20need%20about%208%2C000%20feet%20to%20hit%20the%20skies%20comfortably%20at%20max%20payload.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20appears%20to%20have%20only%20released%20renderings%20of%20the%20Windrunner%2C%20and%20it's%20unclear%20if%20it's%20built%20the%20aircraft%20or%20any%20prototypes.%20Radia's%20press%20team%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222798%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rendering%20of%20a%20fleet%20of%20Radia's%20WindRunner%20cargo%20planes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F660151e61caec1275a68dc38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221844%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERendering%20of%20a%20fleet%20of%20Radia's%20WindRunner%20cargo%20planes.%3Cp%3ERadia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Radia%20announced%20a%20research%20partnership%20with%20the%20US%20Transportation%20Command%20in%20May