0stuck%20outside%20the%20US%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Microsoft%2C%20which%20applied%20for%20more%20than%205%2C500%20H-1B%20visas%20in%20fiscal%20year%202024%2C%20the%20order%20triggered%20instant%20turmoil.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20going%20to%20rock%20our%20shit%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20employee%20told%20Business%20Insider%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity.%20%26quot%3BThe%20number%20of%20H-1Bs%20we%20use%20is%20very%20high%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20H-1Bs%20our%20partners%20and%20contractors%20use%20is%20also%20very%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20that%20imposed%20a%20%24100%2C000%20fee%20on%20H-1B%20visas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68d068d5f9db348adc0be44d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20that%20imposed%20a%20%24100%2C000%20fee%20on%20H-1B%20visas%3Cp%3EDemetrius%20Freeman%2FThe%20Washington%20Post%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%20night%2C%20Microsoft%20sent%20out%20a%20warning%20to%20employees%3A%20%26quot%3BBeginning%20at%2012%3A01%20a.m.%20eastern%20time%20on%20September%2021%2C%20individuals%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20enter%2Freturn%20to%20the%20U.S.%20in%20H-1B%20status%20unless%20their%20petition%20has%20an%20additional%20%24100%2C000%20payment%20associated%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20internal%20memo%20viewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20states.%20It%20advised%20those%20already%20in%20the%20country%20to%20%26quot%3Bremain%20in%20the%20U.S.%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future%26quot%3B%20and%20those%20abroad%20to%20%26quot%3Bdo%20what%20you%20can%26quot%3B%20to%20return%20before%20the%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Trump%20administration%20gave%20no%20real%20advance%20warning%20on%20the%20proclamation%2C%20and%20so%20everyone%20is%20reacting%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Microsoft%20executive%20who%20wished%20to%20stay%20anonymous%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20shocked%20and%20confused.%20There's%20a%20lot%20of%20anxiety.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20canceled%20travel%20plans%20or%20rushed%20back.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESherin%20Sunny%2C%20a%20senior%20software%20engineering%20manager%20at%20Walmart%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fh1b-visa-holders-big-tech-last-anxiety-trump-eo-india-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Business%20Insider%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20the%2036%20hours%20following%20Trump's%20order%20were%20filled%20with%20panic%20and%20fear.%20He%20was%20constantly%20checking%20YouTube%2C%20LinkedIn%2C%20and%20the%20White%20House%20official%20channels%20for%20clearer%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle's%20immigration%20lawyers%20also%20spent%20Friday%20night%20trying%20to%20understand%20the%20order%20and%20alert%20employees%20that%20they%20were%20monitoring%20the%20situation.%20Employees%20on%20H-1Bs%20who%20were%20in%20the%20US%20were%20advised%20to%20remain%20in%20the%20US%2C%20while%20those%20outside%20of%20the%20country%20were%20told%20they%20should%20do%20their%20best%20to%20re-enter%20the%20US%20by%2012%3A01%20a.m.%20on%20Sunday.%20In%202024%2C%20Google%20applied%20for%20nearly%205%2C500%20H-1B%20visas%20for%20its%20employees%2C%20according%20to%20USCIS%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeparting%20the%20U.S.%20may%20result%20in%20complications%20or%20denial%20of%20re-entry%20under%20the%20new%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20an%20email%20to%20Googlers%20sent%20by%20BAL%2C%20the%20company's%20immigration%20law%20firm.%20Googlers%20outside%20the%20country%20who%20might%20not%20make%20it%20back%20by%20the%20deadline%20were%20told%20to%20alert%20someone%20via%20Google's%20internal%20immigration%20portal.%20%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20this%20may%20create%20challenges%2C%20and%20w