22Photo%20collage%20of%20Elon%20Musk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689cf056a17a8c5b4052d419%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESome%20workers%20who%20train%20xAI's%20chatbot%20said%20they've%20encountered%20NSFW%20content%2C%20including%20child%20sexual%20abuse.%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3B%20Grok%2FxAI%3B%5CtKent%20Nishimura%2FGetty%3B%20Tyler%20Le%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20xAI%20workers%20said%20they've%20encountered%20NSFW%20content%2C%20including%20AI-generated%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20material.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGrok%20has%20several%20provocative%20functions.%20Experts%20say%20they%20could%20make%20it%20more%20difficult%20to%20weed%20out%20illegal%20sexual%20content.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EXAI%20is%20one%20of%20many%20AI%20companies%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20eliminate%20AI-generated%20CSAM.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-ceo-elon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E's%20xAI%20has%20designed%20its%20Grok%20chatbot%20to%20be%20deliberately%20provocative.%20It%20has%20a%20flirtatious%20female%20avatar%20that%20can%20strip%20on%20command%2C%20a%20chatbot%20that%20toggles%20between%20%26quot%3Bsexy%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bunhinged%26quot%3B%20modes%2C%20and%20an%20image%20and%20video%20generation%20feature%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bspicy%26quot%3B%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20who%20train%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-org-chart-employees-elon-musk-direct-reports-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ExAI's%20chatbot%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20seen%20firsthand%20what%20it%20means%20to%20carry%20out%20this%20vision.%20In%20conversations%20with%20more%20than%2030%20current%20and%20former%20workers%20across%20a%20variety%20of%20projects%2C%2012%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20encountered%20sexually%20explicit%20material%20%E2%80%94%20including%20instances%20of%20user%20requests%20for%20AI-generated%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20content%20(CSAM).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESexual%20material%20and%20CSAM%20crop%20up%20across%20nearly%20every%20major%20tech%20platform%2C%20but%20experts%20say%20xAI%20has%20made%20explicit%20content%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrok-artificial-intelligence-chatbot-elon-musk-xai-explained-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrok's%20DNA%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20ways%20that%20set%20it%20apart.%20Unlike%20OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20Meta%2C%20which%20largely%20block%20sexual%20requests%2C%20xAI's%20strategy%20could%20complicate%20things%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20preventing%20the%20chatbot%20from%20generating%20CSAM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20don't%20draw%20a%20hard%20line%20at%20anything%20unpleasant%2C%20you%20will%20have%20a%20more%20complex%20problem%20with%20more%20gray%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20Riana%20Pfefferkorn%2C%20a%20tech%20policy%20researcher%20at%20Stanford%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20verified%20the%20existence%20of%20multiple%20written%20requests%20for%20CSAM%20from%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20Grok%20users%2C%20including%20requests%20for%20short%20stories%20that%20depicted%20minors%20in%20sexually%20explicit%20situations%20and%20requests%20for%20pornographic%20images%20involving%20children.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20Grok%20had%20produced%20an%20image%20or%20written%20story%20containing%20CSAM%2C%20the%20workers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20said%20that%20they're%20told%20to%20select%20a%20button%20on%20an%20internal%20system%20to%20flag%20CSAM%20or%20other%20illegal%20content%20so%20that%20it%20can%20be%20quarantined%20and%20to%20prevent%20the%20AI%20model%20from%20learning%20how%20to%20generate%20the%20restricted%20content.%20More%20recently%2C%20workers%20have%20been%20told%20they%20should%20also%20alert%20their%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20workers%2C%20including%20the%2012%20who%20said%20they%20encountered%20NSFW%20content%2C%20said%20they%20signed%20various%20agreements%20consenting%20to%20exposure%20to%20sensitive%20material.%20The%20agreements%20covered%20projects%20geared%20toward%20adult%20content%20and%20general%20projects%20that%20involved%20annotating%20Grok's%20overall%20image%20generation%20or%20text%20generation%20capabilities%2C%20as%20explicit%20content%20could%20pop%20up%20at%20random.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20document%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%20said%20that%20workers%20might%20encounter%20the%20following%20content%3A%20%26quot%3BMedia%20content%20depicting%20pre-pubescent%20minors%20victimized%20in%20a%20sexual%20act%2C%20pornographic%20images%20and%2For%20child%20exploitation%3B%20Media%20content%20depicting%20moment-of-death%20of%20an%20individual%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20written%20descriptions%20of%20sexual%20and%20physical%20abuse%2C%20hate%20speech%2C%20violent%20threats%2C%20and%20graphic%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFallon%20McNulty%2C%20executive%20director%20at%20the%20National%20Center%20for%20Missing%20and%20Exploited%20Children%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20companies%20focused%20on%20sexual%20content%20need%20to%20take%20extra%20care%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20preventing%20CSAM%20on%20their%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20company%20is%20creating%20a%20model%20that%20allows%20nudity%20or%20sexually%20explicit%20generations%2C%20that%20is%20much%20more%20nuanced%20than%20a%20model%20that%20has%20hard%20rules%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20to%20take%20really%20strong%20measures%20so%20that%20absolutely%20nothing%20related%20to%20children%20can%20come%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20whether%20the%20volume%20of%20NSFW%20content%20or%20CSAM%20increased%20after%20xAI%20introduced%20its%20%26quot%3BUnhinged%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BSexy%26quot%3B%20Grok%20voice%20functions%20in%20February.%20Like%20other%20AI%20firms%2C%20xAI%20tries%20to%20prevent%20AI-generated%20CSAM.%20Business%20Insider%20was%20unable%20to%20determine%20whether%20xAI%20data%20annotators%20review%20more%20such%20material%20than%20their%20counterparts%20at%20OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20or%20Meta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20previously%20called%20the%20removal%20of%20child%20sexual%20exploitation%20material%20his%20%26quot%3Bpriority%20%231%26quot%3B%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1594548607243411456%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscussing%20platform%20safety%20for%20X.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20that%20trains%20Grok%20has%20had%20a%20tumultuous%20month.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-xai-layoffs-data-annotators-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOver%20500%20workers%20were%20laid%20off%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20several%20high-level%20employees%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-management-shakeup-data-annotation-team-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehad%20their%20Slack%20accounts%20deactivated%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20and%20the%20company%20appears%20to%20be%20moving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-tumultuous-month-job-cuts-leadership-exodus-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaway%20from%20generalists%20toward%20more%20specialized%20hires%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20not%20clear%20if%20the%20shifting%20structure%20of%20the%20team%20will%20change%20its%20training%20protocols.%20Musk%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1968196086193066365%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%20that%20training%20for%20Grok%205%20will%20begin%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20few%20weeks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20xAI%20and%20X%2C%20which%20merged%20with%20xAI%20this%20past%20March%2C%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22671f5dab-fdbc-473e-9df8-d0b149c0039a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Unhinged'%20Grok%20and%20sexy%20avatars%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-elon-musk-hiring-ramp-up-data-annotators-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EXAI's%20tutors%3C%2Fa%3E%20review%20and%20annotate%20hundreds%20of%20images%2C%20videos%2C%20and%20audio%20files%20to%20improve%20Grok's%20performance%20and%20make%20the%20chatbot's%20output%20more%20realistic%20and%20humanlike.%20Like%20content%20moderators%20for%20platforms%20like%20YouTube%20or%20Facebook%2C%20AI%20tutors%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-training-jobs-data-annotators-labelers-outlier-scale-meta-xai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoften%20see%20the%20worst%20of%20the%20internet%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20have%20thick%20skin%20to%20work%20here%2C%20and%20even%20then%20it%20doesn't%20feel%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20former%20worker%20said.%20They%20said%20they%20quit%20this%20year%20over%20concerns%20about%20the%20amount%20of%20CSAM%20they%20encountered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20tutors%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20NSFW%20content%20has%20been%20difficult%20to%20avoid%20on%20the%20job%2C%20whether%20their%20tasks%20involve%20annotating%20images%2C%20short%20stories%2C%20or%20audio.%20Projects%20originally%20intended%20to%20improve%20Grok's%20tone%20and%20realism%20were%20at%20times%20overtaken%20by%20user%20demand%20for%20sexually%20explicit%20content%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXAI%20has%20asked%20for%20workers%20willing%20to%20read%20semi-pornographic%20scripts%2C%20three%20people%20said.%20The%20company%20has%20also%20asked%20for%20people%20with%20expertise%20in%20porn%20or%20for%20people%20willing%20to%20work%20with%20adult%20content%2C%20five%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20the%20February%20release%20of%20Grok's%20voice%20function%20%E2%80%94%20which%20includes%20%26quot%3Bsexy%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bunhinged%26quot%3B%20versions%20%E2%80%94%20workers%20began%20transcribing%20the%20chatbot's%20conversations%20with%20real-life%20users%2C%20some%20of%20which%20are%20explicit%20in%20nature%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20program%20internally%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3BProject%20Rabbit%2C%26quot%3B%20workers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20tutors%20were%20brought%20into%20Project%20Rabbit.%20It%20briefly%20ended%20this%20spring%2C%20but%20temporarily%20returned%20with%20the%20release%20of%20Grok%20companions%2C%20including%20a%20highly%20sexualized%20character%20named%20%26quot%3BAni%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrok-tesla-vehicles-elon-musk-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20Grok%20app%20for%20some%20Tesla%20owners%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20project%20appeared%20to%20come%20to%20an%20end%20in%20August%2C%20two%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20workers%20with%20knowledge%20of%20the%20project%20said%20it%20was%20initially%20intended%20to%20improve%20the%20chatbot's%20voice%20capabilities%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20sexual%20or%20vulgar%20requests%20quickly%20turned%20it%20into%20an%20NSFW%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20project%20geared%20toward%20teaching%20Grok%20how%20to%20carry%20on%20an%20adult%20conversation%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20workers%20said.%20%26quot%3BThose%20conversations%20can%20be%20sexual%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20designed%20to%20be%20solely%20sexual.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20listened%20to%20some%20pretty%20disturbing%20things.%20It%20was%20basically%20audio%20porn.%20Some%20of%20the%20things%20people%20asked%20for%20were%20things%20I%20wouldn't%20even%20feel%20comfortable%20putting%20in%20Google%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20former%20employee%20who%20worked%20on%20Project%20Rabbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20I%20was%20eavesdropping%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Blike%20people%20clearly%20didn't%20understand%20that%20there's%20people%20on%20the%20other%20end%20listening%20to%20these%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProject%20Rabbit%20was%20split%20into%20two%20teams%20called%20%26quot%3BRabbit%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BFluffy.%26quot%3B%20The%20latter%20was%20designed%20to%20be%20more%20child-friendly%20and%20teach%20Grok%20how%20to%20communicate%20with%20children%2C%20two%20workers%20said.%20Musk%20has%20said%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20release%20a%20child-friendly%20AI%20companion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20worker%20who%20was%20assigned%20to%20an%20image-based%20initiative%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-grok-training-bias-woke-idealogy-2025-02%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BProject%20Aurora%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20the%20overall%20content%2C%20particularly%20some%20of%20the%20images%20they%20had%20to%20review%2C%20made%20them%20feel%20%26quot%3Bdisgusting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20former%20workers%20said%20the%20company%20held%20a%20meeting%20about%20the%20number%20of%20requests%20for%20CSAM%20in%20the%20image%20training%20project.%20During%20the%20meeting%2C%20xAI%20told%20tutors%20the%20requests%20were%20coming%20from%20real-life%20Grok%20users%2C%20the%20workers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20actually%20made%20me%20sick%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20former%20worker%20said.%20%26quot%3BHoly%20shit%2C%20that's%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20looking%20for%20that%20kind%20of%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20can%20opt%20out%20of%20any%20project%20or%20choose%20to%20skip%20an%20inappropriate%20image%20or%20clip%2C%20and%20one%20former%20worker%20said%20that%20higher-ups%20have%20said%20workers%20would%20not%20be%20penalized%20for%20choosing%20to%20avoid%20a%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20several%20hundred%20employees%20opted%20out%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-grok-training-facial-expressions-skippy-employees-react-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BProject%20Skippy%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20required%20employees%20to%20record%20videos%20of%20themselves%20and%20grant%20the%20company%20access%20to%20use%20of%20their%20likeness%2C%20according%20to%20screenshots%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20before%20the%20mass%20opt-outs%20of%20Project%20Skippy%2C%20six%20workers%20said%20that%20declining%20to%20participate%20in%20projects%20could%20be%20difficult.%20They%20said%20it%20required%20them%20to%20reject%20assignments%20from%20their%20team%20lead%2C%20which%20they%20worried%20could%20result%20in%20termination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFour%20other%20former%20workers%20said%20the%20company's%20human%20resources%20team%20narrowed%20the%20flexibility%20for%20opting%20out%20in%20an%20announcement%20on%20Slack%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2255debf04-c788-46ab-89c3-588775817b06%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'They%20should%20be%20very%20cautious'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20AI%20boom%2C%20regulators%20have%20seen%20an%20uptick%20in%20reports%20of%20AI-generated%20content%20involving%20child%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20and%20it%20has%20become%20a%20growing%20issue%20across%20the%20industry.%20Lawmakers%20are%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20address%20a%20variety%20of%20AI-generated%20content%2C%20whether%20it's%20purely%20fictional%20content%20or%20an%20individual%20using%20AI%20to%20alter%20real-life%20images%20of%20children%2C%20Pfefferkorn%2C%20the%20Stanford%20researcher%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20ongoing%20class%20action%20complaint%20against%20Scale%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20which%20provides%20training%20and%20data%20annotation%20services%20to%20major%20tech%20firms%20like%20Alphabet%20and%20Meta%20%E2%80%94%20workers%20accused%20the%20company%20of%20violating%20federal%20worker%20safety%20laws%20by%20subjecting%20contractors%20to%20distressing%20content.%20In%202023%2C%20Time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F6247678%2Fopenai-chatgpt-kenya-workers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20OpenAI%20was%20using%20data%20annotators%20in%20Kenya%20to%20review%20content%20that%20included%20depictions%20of%20violent%20acts%20and%20CSAM.%20Spokespeople%20for%20OpenAI%20and%20Meta%20said%20the%20companies%20don't%20allow%20content%20that%20harms%20children%20on%20their%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20AI%20companies%20have%20safety%20teams%20that%20perform%20a%20task%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-gpt4-openai-answer-creepy-dangerous-murder-bomb-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bred%20teaming%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20process%20dedicated%20to%20pushing%20AI%20models%20to%20the%20limit%20to%20guard%20against%20malicious%20actors%20that%20could%20prompt%20the%20chatbots%20to%20generate%20illegal%20content%2C%20from%20bomb-making%20guides%20to%20pornographic%20content%20involving%20minors.%20In%20April%2C%20xAI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-elon-musk-grok-red-team-hiring-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%20several%20roles%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20involved%20red%20teaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllowing%20an%20AI%20model%20to%20train%20off%20illegal%20material%20would%20be%20risky%2C%20Dani%20Pinter%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20and%20director%20of%20the%20Law%20Center%20for%20the%20National%20Center%20on%20Sexual%20Exploitation%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BFor%20training%20reasons%20alone%2C%20they%20should%20be%20very%20cautious%20about%20letting%20that%20type%20of%20content%20in%20their%20machine%20learning%20portal%2C%26quot%3B%20Pinter%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it's%20important%20the%20chatbots%20are%20trained%20not%20to%20spit%20back%20CSAM%20in%20response%20to%20user%20requests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20drum%20we're%20beating%20right%20now%20is%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20practice%20corporate%20responsibility%20and%20implementing%20safety%20with%20innovation%2C%26quot%3B%20Pinter%20said.%20%26quot%3BCompanies%20can't%20be%20recklessly%20innovating%20without%20safety%2C%20especially%20with%20tools%20that%20can%20involve%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENCMEC%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncmec.org%2Fblog%2F2025%2Fspike-in-online-crimes-against-children-a-wake-up-call%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblog%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20early%20September%20that%20it%20began%20tracking%20reports%20of%20AI-generated%20CSAM%20in%202023%20from%20social%20media%20sites%20and%20saw%20a%20surge%20in%20reports%20from%20AI%20companies%20last%20year.%20Companies%20are%20strongly%20encouraged%20to%20report%20these%20requests%20to%20the%20agency%2C%20even%20if%20the%20content%20doesn't%20depict%20real%20children.%20The%20Department%20of%20Justice%20has%20already%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Farchives%2Fopa%2Fpr%2Fman-arrested-producing-distributing-and-possessing-ai-generated-images-minors-engaged%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epursuing%3C%2Fa%3E%20cases%20involving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Farchives%2Fopa%2Fpr%2Farmy-soldier-arrested-using-ai-generate-child-pornography%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-generated%20CSAM%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20OpenAI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncmec.org%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2Fmissingkids%2Fpdfs%2Fcybertiplinedata2024%2F2024-reports-by-esp.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%2032%2C000%20instances%20of%20CSAM%20to%20NCMEC%2C%20and%20Anthropic%20reported%20971.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpokespeople%20for%20Anthropic%20and%20OpenAI%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20companies%20don't%20allow%20CSAM%20and%20have%20strict%20policies%20in%20place%20to%20prevent%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXAI%20did%20not%20file%20any%20reports%20in%202024%2C%20according%20to%20the%20organization.%20NCMEC%20told%20Business%20Insider%20it%20has%20not%20received%20any%20reports%20from%20xAI%20so%20far%20this%20year.%20It%20said%20it%20has%20received%20reports%20of%20potentially%20AI-generated%20CSAM%20from%20X%20Corp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENCMEC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.missingkids.org%2Fgethelpnow%2Fcybertipline%2Fcybertiplinedata%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20received%20about%2067%2C000%20reports%20involving%20generative%20AI%20in%202024%2C%20compared%20with%204%2C700%20the%20year%20before.%20In%20the%20blog%20published%20last%20week%2C%20the%20organization%20said%20it%20had%20already%20received%20440%2C419%20reports%20of%20AI-generated%20CSAM%20as%20of%20June%2030%2C%20compared%20with%205%2C976%20during%20the%20same%20period%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20for%20xAI%20or%20have%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Agkay%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Egkay%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20248-894-6012.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20device%2C%20and%20nonwork%20WiFi%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-grok-explicit-content-data-annotation-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1758460972000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F689cf056a17a8c5b4052d419%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsi