bitats%E2%80%9D.%20These%20enable%20the%20animals%20to%20disperse%2C%20reduce%20their%20risk%20of%20separation%20and%20make%20habitat%20rehabilitation%20easier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20explored%20how%20anthropogenic%20stress%2C%20the%20development%20of%20roads%20and%20railways%2C%20and%20hydroelectric%20projects%20are%20hampering%20these%20corridors.%20The%20problem%20is%20compounded%20by%20multiple%20forests%20being%20turned%20into%20croplands%20by%20the%20farming%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-500x417.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20walking%20bear%20cubs%20to%20reintroducing%20orphaned%20elephant%20calves%20back%20into%20the%20wild%2C%20Vivek%20Menon%20is%20championing%20wildlife%20conservation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-500x417.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-300x250.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-768x641.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-1536x1281.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-1200x1001.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275-150x125.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Ayushman-and-Peter-walking-Bear-cubs-Tawang-and-Tawangi-near-Bhalunala-camp-Pakke-TR-Arunachal-Pradesh_March-2021_Amrit-Menon_11zon-1-1723468275.jpeg%201822w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360936%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22417%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFrom%20walking%20bear%20cubs%20to%20reintroducing%20orphaned%20elephant%20calves%20back%20into%20the%20wild%2C%20Vivek%20Menon%20is%20championing%20wildlife%20conservation%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vivek%20Menon%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2025%20years%2C%20WTI%20has%20attempted%20to%20better%20the%20narrative%20for%20wildlife%20across%20species.%20Their%20impact%20is%20resounding%20%E2%80%94%20campaigning%20for%20the%20whale%20shark%20to%20be%20made%20the%20first%20fish%20to%20be%20protected%20under%20the%20Wildlife%20(Protection)%20Act%2C%201972%2C%20in%20India%2C%20exposing%20the%20illegal%20mongoose%20hairbrush%20trade%2C%20assisting%20in%20the%20seizure%20of%20over%20275%20wildlife%20articles%20including%20tiger%20bones%20and%20bear%20bile%2C%20and%20the%20inception%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F65156%2Fpangolin-conservation-wildlife-sos%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epangolin%20trafficking%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20attempts%20to%20curb%20illegal%20trade%20of%20the%20species.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20organisation%20masks%20its%20humble%20beginnings.%20But%20Vivek%20Menon%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20forgotten%20these.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20as%20a%20team%20of%20three%20people%20in%20a%20spare%20room%20of%20my%20house.%20Each%20of%20us%20invested%20Rs%205%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20The%20investment%20was%20secondary.%20Passion%20was%20what%20drove%20WTI%20to%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMenon%20has%20a%20piece%20of%20advice%20that%20he%20believes%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20ensuring%20a%20better%20place%20for%20wildlife%2C%20including%20elephants%2C%20on%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFirm%20anti-poaching%20policies%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20spent%20the%20better%20part%20of%20his%20life%20as%20a%20conservationist%20training%20Indian%20forest%20guards%2C%20rangers%2C%20and%20paramilitary%20forces%20on%20anti-poaching%20activities%20and%20smuggling%20techniques%2C%20Menon%20has%20witnessed%20the%20network%20close%20up.%20But%20he%20insists%20that%2C%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20any%20illegal%20activity%2C%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20way%20of%20curbing%20it%20completely.%20%E2%80%9COne%20can%20only%20lessen%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20end%2C%20Menon%20says%20the%20forest%20guards%20are%20often%20the%20first%20line%20of%20defence%20to%20stop%20illegal%20trade.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20should%20be%20trained%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F233468%2Findia-tigers-save-vultures-how-to-wildlife-conservation-environment-rajasthan-ranthambhore-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eanti-poaching%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%20He%20adds%20that%20in%20cases%20of%20the%20animal%20being%20poached%20despite%20precautionary%20measures%2C%20the%20border%20staff%20should%20be%20trained%20to%20ensure%20that%20smuggling%20of%20ivory%20is%20not%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReducing%20man-animal%20conflict%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECrop%20raiding%20and%20property%20destruction%20are%20the%20prime%20factors%20that%20cause%20elephant-human%20conflict%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EInternational%20Fund%20for%20Animal%20Welfare%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20study%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%20in%20India%2C%20100%20elephants%20die%20annually%20from%20conflict%20with%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation-1_11zon-1723468410.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20creating%20elephant%20corridors%20across%20India%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation-1_11zon-1723468410.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation-1_11zon-1723468410-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation-1_11zon-1723468410-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation-1_11zon-1723468410-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2Felephant-protection-and-preservation-1_11zon-1723468410-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360941%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20creating%20elephant%20corridors%20across%20India%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Vivek%20Menon%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%2C%20says%20Menon%2C%20is%20exacerbated%20by%20lack%20of%20space.%20%E2%80%9CAn%20elephant%20is%20a%20big%2C%20intelligent%20social%20nomad.%20It%20has%20to%20move%3B%20it%20has%20to%20do%20so%20in%20groups%3B%20and%20it%20is%20intelligent.%20Whatever%20stands%20in%20its%20way%20it%20will%20destroy%20to%20move.%20One%20has%20to%20respect%20it%20and%20give%20it%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreate%20elephant%20corridors%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20perfect%20world%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F141120%2Fwildlife-sos-bears-elephants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehabitats%20of%20elephants%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20contiguous%2C%20Menon%20points%20out.%20%E2%80%9CElephants%20would%20be%20able%20to%20move%20from%20the%20Himalayas%20to%20the%20South%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%20But%20he%20adds%20that%20the%20reason%20this%20is%20no%20longer%20possible%20is%20because%20the%20mammals%20now%20share%20the%20ground%20with%20people%20and%20their%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20WTI%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20demarcate%20the%20elephant%20corridors%20and%20push%20for%20them%20to%20be%20declared%20as%20protected%20zones%2C%20Menon%20says%2C%20they%20relied%20on%20elephant%20footpaths.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20mapped%20these%20and%20showed%20it%20in%20a%20publication%2C%20explaining%20why%20they%20were%20integral%20pieces%20of%20land%20that%20connected%20with%20the%20different%20habitats.%20We%20delineated%20these%20on%20paper%2C%20asking%20the%20Government%20to%20protect%20these%20elephant%20corridors.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20learnings%20they%20had%20during%20the%20project%2C%20Menon%20says%20the%20protection%20of%20elephant%20corridors%20can%20be%20done%20in%20four%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20model%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20the%20community%20model%20in%20the%20Northeast%2C%20which%20has%20been%20on%20for%20the%20past%20two%20decades.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20model%20focuses%20on%20land%20being%20kept%20aside%20by%20the%20community%20for%20elephants%20to%20move.%20It%20also%20involves%20rewarding%20the%20community%20with%20some%20benefits%2C%E2%80%9D%20Menon%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20model%20is%20pushing%20the%20Government%20to%20acquire%20land%20and%20conduct%20linear%20infrastructure%20mitigations.%20The%20third%2C%20he%20says%2C%20is%20to%20create%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F180063%2Fkerala-woman-animal-rights-elephants-inspirational%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20community%20of%20people%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20are%20trained%20in%20keeping%20an%20eye%20out%20for%20elephant%20movements.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20in%20Kaziranga%2C%20there%20are%20groups%20of%20young%20boys%20who%20are%20on%20alert.%20They%20stop%20cars%20to%20allow%20the%20elephants%20to%20cross.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20is%20to%20relocate%20villages.%20This%20%E2%80%9Clast-ditch%20effort%E2%80%9D%20is%20only%20resorted%20to%20in%20areas%20where%20people%20have%20settled%20right%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20elephant%20corridors%20and%20elephants%20are%20killing%20them%20and%20not%20letting%20crops%20grow%2C%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-Executive-Director-Wildlife-Trust-of-India_11zon-1723468527-500x672.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vivek%20Menon%20and%20elephants%20share%20a%20bond%20of%20love%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FVivek-Menon-Founder-E