le%20zinc%20and%20bring%20it%20to%20the%20roots.%20This%20increases%20zinc%20base%20levels%20to%2050-55%20parts%20per%20million%20%E2%80%93%20an%20increment%20of%20about%2080%20percent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20every%20seed%20will%20have%20its%20own%20benefits%20and%20drawbacks.%20These%20seeds%20give%20almost%2080%20percent%20more%20nutritional%20value%20but%20farmers%20may%20have%20to%20take%20a%20dip%20of%204%20to%205%20percent%20in%20yield.%20But%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349986%2Fprabhat-kumar-sumarth-ngo-bihar-horticulture-training-for-farmers-double-income-cash-crops%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epremium%20rates%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20such%20produce%20covers%20up%20the%20yield%20loss%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20collaborations%20with%20thousands%20of%20farmers%20across%20regions%20like%20Gorakhpur%2C%20Basti%2C%20Gonda%2C%20Barabanki%2C%20and%20others%2C%20the%20initiative%20not%20only%20promoted%20the%20adoption%20of%20biofortified%20seeds%20but%20also%20provided%20holistic%20services%20ranging%20from%20soil%20analysis%20to%20crop%20selection%20in%20order%20to%20boost%20crop%20nutrient%20content%20naturally.%20Greenday%20has%20achieved%20an%20annual%C2%A0turnover%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20impact%20created%20by%20their%20startup%2C%20Aishwarya%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20spending%202.5%20years%20in%20Sitapur%20closely%20working%20with%20farmers%2C%20I%20saw%20the%20potential%20in%20something%20as%20small%20as%20a%20seed.%20We%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20massive%20impact%20by%20working%20for%20our%20farmers.%20Seeing%20their%20dedication%20first%20hand%20has%20been%20the%20most%20rewarding%20experience.%20Their%20hard%20work%20fuels%20our%20passion%20to%20turn%20our%20brand%20into%20a%20movement%20that%20not%20only%20improves%20health%20but%20also%20supports%20livelihoods%2C%E2